== Overview ==
Using the same reactive power as seen in the [[Magma Cannon]] and [[Morning Star]], the powerful Magmatic reactor offers a lighter weight, high end power source.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Magmatic Reactor can be bought in the workshop after obtaining [[Magma Technology]].

